    • addCalculatePowerLimitListeners

      static void addCalculatePowerLimitListeners(Evcs evcs)
      Adds onSetNextValue listeners for minimum and maximum hardware power.

      Since the minimum and maximum power strongly depends on the connected vehicle, this automatically adjusts it to the currently used phases.

      Parameters:
      evcs - evcs
